{"tid":1802362,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個wrong timing嘅經歷","createTime":"2019-12-29T11:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T17:24:19.000Z","uid":205742,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"80325063ba1a6f24cfff0a753cc5cd22b22ac2d6","tid":1802362,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"有一晚凌晨佢打電話比我，問覺得我哋夾唔夾，我都比佢嚇親，冇諗過大家咁快，之後又話佢太過佢自己個星座同我唔夾，佢同佢ex都係星座唔夾咁，之後叫我睇啲乜嘢濕鳩生日書，仲叫我讀比佢聽，但因為我發誓唔會再用電話表白，所以當時冇講其他嘢，只係答覺得大家夾，一凹一凸咁<br />\n<br />\n然之後...... 佢之後果日就飛咗去台灣... 一個星期之後返嚟見個時都好地地，有好多身體接觸，但走咗之後就text我話：「唔好鍾意我 我想同你繼續做朋友」<br />\n<br />\n如果當時佢唔係去旅行 可能我之後嗰日已經可以同到佢一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n世事就係咁撚柒戇鳩 啱嘅timing真係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f22c000801c7488b1d41517c0f1cc58067edfda","tid":1802362,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:56:17.000Z","msg":"好可惜..."},{"pid":"e7de0ab47e55c7fa46e9d0ee5eac767c23925640","tid":1802362,"uid":132174,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:01:41.000Z","msg":"去旅行都叫timing唔啱..."},{"pid":"54ba0d7c13544a5c26040190e3b0dc3298f4aacd","tid":1802362,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"e7de0ab47e55c7fa46e9d0ee5eac767c23925640","tid":1802362,"uid":132174,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:01:41.000Z","msg":"去旅行都叫timing唔啱..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:17:31.000Z","msg":"咁都唔叫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee67485ec1e933cce6f0d852621a40ad78f3c74","tid":1802362,"uid":59192,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:20:39.000Z","msg":"一個星期既時間咋喎<br />\n唔係一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b79b504ae035dcc295951b7b6606a244277b73","tid":1802362,"uid":331192,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T1